stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Start
    Start --> ReadFile : open workflow-delegation.md
    ReadFile --> InsertFormatRules : locate insertion point (line 117)
    InsertFormatRules --> AddContaminationGuard : append format rule to Common Constraints
    AddContaminationGuard --> VerifyLineCount : count total lines
    VerifyLineCount --> End : line count <= 200
    VerifyLineCount --> TrimContent : line count > 200
    TrimContent --> VerifyLineCount : re-check after trimming
    End --> [*]

    Start : Initialize implementation phase
    ReadFile : ConfirmCurrentLines then IdentifyInsertPoint
    InsertFormatRules : CreateHeading then AddSixRules
    AddContaminationGuard : Append guard line to constraints
    VerifyLineCount : RunWordCount then CompareThreshold
    TrimContent : Condense or remove excess content
    End : All F-NNN requirements verified

    note right of Start : Entry point for implementation
    note left of TrimContent : Triggered only if exceeding 200 lines
